00:36:36,140 --> 00:36:40,760
中文字幕
Then below the head, but inside the html tag still, was my body.

783
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,810
中文字幕
So let me type that here.

784
00:36:41,810 --> 00:36:43,790
中文字幕
And I think I said, "hello, body."

