1255
00:57:43,450 --> 00:57:47,830
中文字幕
And it turns out that inside of a form, you can have different tags as well--

1256
00:57:47,830 --> 00:57:49,450
中文字幕
specifically, an input.

1257
00:57:49,450 --> 00:57:50,710
中文字幕
And inputs have names.

1258
00:57:50,710 --> 00:57:55,450
中文字幕
So I can say name equals "q" to mimic Larry and Sergey's decision years ago,

1259
00:57:55,450 --> 00:57:56,650
中文字幕
the founders of Google.

1260
00:57:56,650 --> 00:57:58,330
中文字幕
The type of this input is text.

1261
00:57:58,330 --> 00:58:01,380
中文字幕
So it's not a button or a check box or something like that.

1262
00:58:01,380 --> 00:58:02,090
中文字幕
Those exist, too.

1263
00:58:02,090 --> 00:58:03,170
中文字幕
It's just text.

