1300
00:59:36,580 --> 00:59:37,630
中文字幕
And voila.

1301
00:59:37,630 --> 00:59:40,240
中文字幕
There we have a whole lot of mice search results.

1302
00:59:40,240 --> 00:59:41,830
中文字幕
But why, is the question?

1303
00:59:41,830 --> 00:59:45,790
中文字幕
Well, all I've done is, using HTML and an HTML form,

1304
00:59:45,790 --> 00:59:48,820
中文字幕
is I've generated the prescribed format of a URL,

1305
00:59:48,820 --> 00:59:53,410
中文字幕
calling Google's Search program with a input of q equals mice.

1306
00:59:53,410 --> 00:59:56,050
中文字幕
And now, as an aside, if I did take more inputs,

1307
00:59:56,050 --> 00:59:57,850
中文字幕
