01:03:25,920 --> 01:03:27,630
中文字幕
I can lay out the structure of this page.

1398
01:03:27,630 --> 01:03:29,570
中文字幕
Yes, I have my three separate paragraphs.

1399
01:03:29,570 --> 01:03:30,930
中文字幕
